data.text: @pritybraun @LeenaTailor @etnow @ladygaga I am recognizing this is the 4th production of the same movie. I prefer the 2nd, starring Judy Garland (I have not seen Lady Gaga's rendition). For example, there are lots of Godzilla movies -- but they are not all the same storyline.
@2hazel_eyez @LeenaTailor @etnow @ladygaga Why'd you say this, is it a bad movie or is it the subject of the movie? Just asking out of interest 👌
@LeenaTailor @etnow @ladygaga The coming movie release of #AStarIsBorn will be the 4th release. As much as I like the movie, enough is enough.
